            <thetext>In an editable qx.ui.form.ComboBox if an item is first selected from the popup list, then the textfield is edited then re-selecting the previously selected item does not change the value of the textfield.

The missbehaviour can be tested here: http://demo.qooxdoo.org/html/test/ComboBox_1.html

1) check the &quot;Editable&quot; checkbox.

2) select the item &quot;Item No 1&quot; from the combobox popup list.

3) change the value in the textfield by typing another text

4) reselect the item &quot;Item No 1&quot; from the combobox popup list.

As you see the value did not change to &quot;Item No 1&quot;. The text typed in at point 3) remains in the textfield.

If another Item is selected (eg. &quot;Item No 2&quot;) then the value is correctly changed. After this you can reselect &quot;Item No 1&quot; which is now in the textfield.</thetext>
